gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Kings 114, Suns 106
gameRecap.excerpt: The Kings defeated the Suns, 114-106. DeAaron Fox scored 23 of game-high 34 points in the fourth quarter along with seven assists and four rebounds as Domantas Sabonis added 15 points, 17 rebounds, and five assists for Sacramento. Devin Booker led Phoenix with 28 points (10-14 FG), seven rebounds, and seven assists. The Kings improve to 12-8 as the Suns move to 12-10.
